<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Resume - Liva Ramarolahy</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #fefce8;
    }
    .container {
      width: 600px;
      background-color: white;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .header {
      background: #E07A5F;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      opacity: 0.95;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .summary-section {
      background-color: #f7fafc;
      border-left: 4px solid #E07A5F;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .summary-section h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #2d3748;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .summary-content {
      color: #4a5568;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .meta-info {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f7fafc;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #718096;
    }
    .meta-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
    }
    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #E07A5F;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .attachment-note {
      background-color: #edf2f7;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      color: #4a5568;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px 30px;
      background-color: #f7fafc;
      text-align: center;
      color: #718096;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #3b82f6;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Interactive Resume</h1>
      <p>Liva Ramarolahy - Full Stack Developer</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="greeting">
        Hello,
      </div>

      <p>Thank you for your interest in my profile! As requested, I'm sending you my resume along with a summary of our conversation.</p>

      @if(conversationSummary)
      <div class="summary-section">
        <h2>Conversation Summary</h2>
        <div class="summary-content">
          {!! conversationSummary !!}
        </div>
      </div>
      @end

      <div class="attachment-note">
         <strong>Resume attached:</strong> cv-ramarolahy.pdf
      </div>

      <p>Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or would like to discuss potential opportunities. I look forward to hearing from you!</p>

      <div class="cta">
        <a href="{{ appUrl }}" class="btn">Continue Our Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent from my Interactive Resume platform.</p>
      <p>© {{ year }} Liva Ramarolahy. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p><a href="{{ appUrl }}">{{ appUrl }}</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>